{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "第六回「十八柄刀」摘要\n\n小马一行人停歇在狼山岩石上，张聋子以读唇术窥探三名神秘人的对话，得知他们是专门劫掠上山肥羊的狼山匪徒，对轿中女眷垂涎已久。常无意与小马因是否出手相争，常无意冷言相劝，小马却不顾危险跳下岩石救人。八个满身鲜血的人实为狼山伏击者，以苦肉计诱敌，被小马和张聋子轻易制服。返回岩石时，众人发现十八柄鬼头刀已架在每个人脖子上——十八柄刀的威胁将众人困于绝境。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一定是吃人狼。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "香香",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "他…他们真的吃人？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们不一定真的会吃人，至少他们敢吃人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道他们最喜欢吃的是哪种人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "香香",
      "listener": "char_lao_pi",
      "text": "哪…哪种人？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_xiang",
      "text": "女人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_pi",
      "speaker_name": "老皮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_xiang",
      "text": "尤其是那种看起来很好看，嗅起来又很香的女人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "那边三位仁兄好象在说话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "他们在说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这几条肥羊一定癫了，居然敢上狼山。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们居然还坐着轿子来，看样子不但癫得厉害，而且肥得厉害。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是其中好象还有一两个扎手的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看得出是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那个阴阳怪气、象个活僵尸的人就一定很不好对付。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有那个高头大马、好象很神气的人，说不定是个保镖的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人丙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那个瞪着眼睛，看着我们的穷老头，而且已经吓呆了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不管怎样，他们的人总比我们多，我们总得去找些帮手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这两天山上的肥羊来的不少，大家都有买卖做，我们能去找谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不管怎么样，反正他们总跑不了，这票买卖既然是我们先看见的，我们总能占上几成。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人丙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只要那三个女的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是被那些老色狼看见，你只怕连一点都分不到。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人丙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等他们用完了，我再吃肉行不行？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那倒没问题。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人丙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你最好一半红烧，一半清炖，我也有许久没有吃过这么漂亮的肉了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "神秘人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我一定分你三大碗，把你活活胀死。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "这地方很好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "可是……可是我总觉得这地方就象是个箭靶子。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就因这个地方象个箭靶子，所以我才说好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "这地方四面空旷，不管有什么人来，我们都可以一眼就看见了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何况他们暂时好象还找不到帮手，等他们找到时，天已黑了，我们已走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "坐下。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你要谁坐下？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你为什么要我坐下？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "因为你不是来多管闹事的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "可惜我天生就是个喜欢管闲事的人。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "那么你去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "我当然要去。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我可以保证一件事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你死了之后，绝不会有人去替你收尸。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "我喜欢埋在别人的肚子里，至少我总可以埋在别人的肚子里。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "只可惜别人喜欢吃的是女人的肉。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "我的肉也很嫩。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "你看怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "先救伤最轻的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是从哪里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "受伤老者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "狼山…狼人……要钱…要命……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们好好的来狼山做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "受伤老者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "因为……因为……因为……我们要宰你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你就是狼山上的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是吃人狼？还是君子狼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我……我是君子……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他真他妈的是个君子。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "看样子我们好象上了当。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "可是现在看起来，真正上当的还是他们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "这也许只不过因为他们都是君子。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "君子是不是总比较容易上当？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "君子总比较喜欢要人上当。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    }
  ],
